@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_arfako(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.10
    tmp = wp.abs(v2)
    v0 = wp.exp(((v1 + 0.72 * tmp + 0.68) + wp.abs(v1 + 0.95)))
    v2 = ((0.50 * wp.exp(v2 + 0.68)) + 0.32)
    data[tid] = v0
